# Sauce Instruction

If the user says "follow sauce" (where "sauce" is the file name):
1. Start the dev servers.
2. Update the dependencies and libraries.
3. Update the code with the latest libraries if any.
4. Start Vercel CLI.
5. Start Supabase CLI (if applicable/present).
6. Connect MCP if any.
7. After all of these, say exactly: "sauce is sauced, waiting for next command, Sire!"
